OL,3,CGovernment facing revolt over plan to
OL,4,Ccriminalise rough sleeping
OL,6,FThis is a fight the government would
OL,7,Flike to avoid during an election year,
OL,8,FITV News Correspondent Tom Sheldrick
OL,9,Freports
OL,11,FMinisters are facing a revolt from
OL,12,Fmore than 40 Conservative MPs over
OL,13,Fplans to criminalise homelessness.
OL,15,FThe Criminal Justice Bill would allow
OL,16,Fthe police to fine or move on
OL,17,F"nuisance" rough sleepers.
