OL,3,CGovernment facing revolt over plan to
OL,4,Ccriminalise rough sleeping
OL,6,FAccording to the Times newspaper,
OL,7,Fsenior government sources have said
OL,8,Fthe Bill has been "paused" while
OL,9,Fministers negotiate with MPs from both
OL,10,Fthe left and right of the Conservative
OL,11,FParty concerned about the plans.
OL,13,FBusiness minister Kevin Hollinrake,
OL,14,Fmeanwhile, appeared reluctant to say
OL,15,Fwhether he supported the Bill as it
OL,16,Fstands, telling broadcasters it was
OL,17,F"not within my auspices".
