OL,6,FHe also emphasised it was important
OL,7,Fthe government used a raft of support
OL,8,Fmeasures to prevent rough sleeping and
OL,9,Fsaid he was interested to see what
OL,10,FRishi Sunak has planned.
OL,12,FConservative former ministers Sir Iain
OL,13,FDuncan Smith and Damian Green are
OL,14,Famong 10 Tories who have signed a
OL,15,Fseries of amendments to the Bill aimed
OL,16,Fat countering the drive to criminalise
OL,17,Frough sleeping.
