OL,3,CGovernment facing revolt over plan to
OL,4,Ccriminalise rough sleeping
OL,6,FMeasures tabled by Tory MP Bob
OL,7,FBlackman (Harrow East) would seek to
OL,8,Fensure ministers fulfil their promise
OL,9,Fto repeal the Vagrancy Act 1824, the
OL,10,Flaw which currently criminalises rough
OL,11,Fsleeping and begging.
OL,13,FThe government promised to do so when
OL,14,Fit passed the Police, Crime,
OL,15,FSentencing and Courts Act in 2022, but
OL,16,Fonly when it found a suitable
OL,17,Freplacement.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/12
