OL,3,CGovernment facing revolt over plan to
OL,4,Ccriminalise rough sleeping
OL,6,FA second amendment from Mr Blackman
OL,7,Faims to clarify when the police are
OL,8,Fable to use the new powers.
OL,10,FThe amendment says police should be
OL,11,Fgiven guidance that "begging or
OL,12,Fsleeping rough does not in itself
OL,13,Famount to unreasonable conduct", and
OL,14,Finsists officers "should balance
OL,15,Fprotection of the community with
OL,16,Fsensitivity to the problems that cause
OL,17,Fpeople to engage in begging or
OL,18,Fsleeping rough".
