OL,3,CGovernment facing revolt over plan to
OL,4,Ccriminalise rough sleeping
OL,6,FThe Bill was introduced to Parliament
OL,7,Fby Suella Braverman ` who branded
OL,8,Frough sleeping a "lifestyle choice" `
OL,9,Fwhen she was home secretary.
OL,11,FThe Liberal Democrats urged the
OL,12,FGovernment to listen to backbenchers
OL,13,Funhappy with the Bill.
OL,15,FLayla Moran, the Lib Dem MP who
OL,16,Fspearheaded the cross-party campaign
OL,17,Fto scrap the Vagrancy Act, said: "The
OL,18,Fheartless proposals in the Criminal
OL,19,FJustice Bill risk bringing back the
OL,20,FVagrancy Act by the back door.
OL,26,@pD@ROUpD@cO]yD@bOU
