OL,3,CGovernment facing revolt over plan to
OL,4,Ccriminalise rough sleeping
OL,6,F"The Government should listen to their
OL,7,Fown backbenchers and take a
OL,8,Fcompassionate approach to tackling
OL,9,Fhomelessness, instead of stigmatising
OL,10,Fand criminalising rough sleepers.
OL,12,F"Sleeping rough is not a lifestyle
OL,13,Fchoice. Ministers should focus on
OL,14,Ftackling the root causes of this
OL,15,Fcrisis, not scapegoating the victims
OL,16,Fof it."
