OL,3,CGovernment facing revolt over plan to
OL,4,Ccriminalise rough sleeping
OL,6,FMatt Downie, chief executive of
OL,7,FCrisis, the national homelessness
OL,8,Fcharity, urged Home Secretary James
OL,9,FCleverly to "drop these cruel and
OL,10,Funnecessary measures and focus on the
OL,11,Freal solutions" including building
OL,12,Fmore social housing.
OL,14,FHe said: "It should never have been
OL,15,Fgovernment policy to criminalise rough
OL,16,Fsleeping, so we would be thrilled to
OL,17,Fsee the back of these deeply-damaging
OL,18,Fproposals that will do nothing to
OL,19,Fsupport people away from the streets.
OL,26,@qD@MOUsD@OO]vD@JOU
