OL,3,CGovernment facing revolt over plan to
OL,4,Ccriminalise rough sleeping
OL,6,F"Through our frontline services we see
OL,7,Fthe brutality rough sleeping inflicts
OL,8,Fon people's lives. With more and more
OL,9,Fpeople being pushed to the brink from
OL,10,Fthe increased cost of living, we need
OL,11,Fa compassionate approach, not one that
OL,12,Fthreatens people with fines or
OL,13,Fimprisonment."
OL,15,FA government spokesperson said: "We
OL,16,Fare determined to end rough sleeping
OL,17,Ffor good. That is why we have
OL,18,Fpublished a strategy to tackle the
OL,19,Froot causes of why people end up on
OL,20,Fthe streets, backed by an
OL,21,Funprecedented #2.4 billion.
